{"tid":897390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雙11】縮衣節食只為「雙11」　強國女大生天天吃泡麵","createTime":"2018-11-10T23:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T04:16:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"de9c215a7ab80e44de1b5dbca7816a408652aa42","tid":897390,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T23:48:21.000Z","msg":"今天是中國網購特價日「雙11」，許多人摩拳擦掌準備搶購優惠商品。中國大陸一名女大生為了準備足夠「銀彈」，連續3周都只吃泡麵。但她也說，等到雙11後，她再也不想看見泡麵。 江蘇南通女大生洪佳表示，為了省錢買到心愛貨品，自10月15日開始，她每餐只吃泡麵，偶爾加上香腸當配料。自己每日記錄所有消費，截至上周一（11日)為止、近3周來，她只花了251元人民幣（約1112元台幣)，還剩下749元人民幣（約3319元台幣）生活費，打算用來買化妝品、面膜之類的商品。她坦承，雙11過後，自己再也不想看到桌上的泡麵。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rwJrwY0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrwJrwY0.png&h=d7163fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181111/1464284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181111%2F1464284&d=sNen2yVoKTn41SYSHAf7BC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=4dc48fb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181111%2F1464284&h=ed367138\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181111/1464284</a>"},{"pid":"379c103d5631b6bd56a28a332e84ccf5e3c24382","tid":897390,"uid":49392,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T23:51:55.000Z","msg":"慳錢買支國貨定假貨呢"},{"pid":"3d13b28bb65d6ed08aac82ba1263509b41324560","tid":897390,"uid":64009,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T00:00:18.000Z","msg":"佢個樣點化妝都無用啦"},{"pid":"26c9af58c1971ee8e0073097629490a171a42a30","tid":897390,"uid":133427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T00:04:02.000Z","msg":"D大陸女人成日都食垃圾（加有毒）食物，用埋有毒化妝品<br />\n唔怪得一兩二個塊面都出晒毒瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad2e89758c5b060608906fb93608f4e6666